{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781144117998,"sessionID":"ses_14b8a0217ffeP6eGAP16BZOkoX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_BjDuEqv3pB0S3o9D6bWkpkJZ","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/015-storage-adapter-ports\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/015-storage-adapter-ports/review/lineages/gpt-2\n  session_id: fanout-gpt-2-1781144091708-itpir0\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.maxIterations: 6\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/015-storage-adapter-ports/review/lineages/gpt-2 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/015-storage-adapter-ports/review/lineages/gpt-2. Do not touch any path outside .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/015-storage-adapter-ports/review/lineages/gpt-2.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt-2","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/015-storage-adapter-ports","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt-2-1781144091708-itpir0","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt-2-1781144091708-itpir0\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt-2-1781144091708-itpir0\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt-2-1781144091708-itpir0\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 223,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781144114888,"end":1781144117996}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0778f5824dcb414e016a2a1a2aee508191bedfb23bdf8d804a"}},"id":"prt_eb476385c001J95dW2UiY8oUl6","sessionID":"ses_14b8a0217ffeP6eGAP16BZOkoX","messageID":"msg_eb47601d5001FFrcD49PEv6d16"}}
