t the original upsert record id.\",\"alternativeExplanation\":\"The better-sqlite adapter may intentionally expose generated memory IDs rather than caller-provided IDs for legacy compatibility. That still leaves the typed port and fake contract ambiguous, so the finding remains P1 against REQ-002 contract validation rather than a current production P0.\",\"finalSeverity\":\"P1\",\"confidence\":0.86,\"downgradeTrigger\":\"Downgrade to P2 if the VectorStore interface explicitly documents generated-ID semantics and the fake plus contract tests are updated to validate that behavior.\",\"transitions\":[{\"iteration\":3,\"from\":null,\"to\":\"P1\",\"reason\":\"Initial discovery during traceability protocol review.\"}]}],\"coverage\":{\"dimensionsCovered\":[\"correctness\",\"security\",\"traceability\"],\"requiredProtocolsCovered\":true},\"noveltyJustification\":\"First direct spec-code/checklist evidence pass found a required contract-coverage gap.\",\"ruledOut\":[\"No missing port exports found in index.ts.\",\"No checklist.md exists because this is Level 1; tasks.md and implementation-summary.md are the completion evidence surfaces.\"],\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt-2-1781144091708-itpir0\",\"generation\":1,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-11T04:21:00.000Z\",\"durationMs\":480000,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.5-fast\"}}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"claim_adjudication\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":3,\"passed\":true,\"packets\":[{\"findingId\":\"F001\",\"finalSeverity\":\"P1\",\"confidence\":0.86}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-11T04:21:05.000Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt-2-1781144091708-itpir0\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":4,\"iteration\":4,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"maintainability\",\"dimensions\":[\"maintainability\"],\"filesReviewed\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/ports/index.ts\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/mem